help.dmGeneral:
**Alliance HQ bot** — run `/help` in your alliance server for steps matched to your role.

Quick list: `/link`, `/link-commander`, `/vr`, `/immunity`, `/who-is-conductor`, `/language`. Owners set up with `/link-alliance`. Officers (R4+): `/vr-report`, `/set-conductor`, `/train-is-ready`.

**Full setup guide:** {guideUrl}

